# Why Indobase Sites is an ideal fit for Astro

## 1. Free hosting with no upfront costs

For developers and small teams, keeping hosting expenses low is important. Indobase Sites provides free hosting, eliminating financial barriers while ensuring a high-performance infrastructure. This allows you to focus on building and refining your application without worrying about costs as you scale.

