Astro shines with its ability to generate highly optimized static sites while enabling selective hydration for dynamic elements. Indobase Sites fully supports static exports, ensuring your site benefits from fast, globally cached delivery. Additionally, **Indobase Functions** can extend Astro's capabilities by adding dynamic backend functionality where necessary.

