Speed is a key factor in both user experience and SEO. Indobase Sites uses a globally distributed [Content Delivery Network (CDN)](/docs/products/network/cdn) to efficiently cache and serve your static assets. This results in reduced latency, faster page loads, and improved site performance across all regions.

