As websites grow, security risks increase. Indobase Sites comes with [DDoS protection](/docs/products/network/ddos), ensuring your application remains online by detecting and mitigating malicious traffic. Additionally, it includes **custom domain management** with automatic SSL encryption, securing your site with minimal setup.

